snippet.title: Hidden Cats in Tokyo - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re thrilled to announce Hidden Cats in Tokyo — the latest adventure from the Hidden Cats franchise! 🐱🔍 Explore the bustling streets of Tokyo and uncover all the hidden cats and secrets!

👀 Teaser now live — stay tuned for more details coming soon!

📢 Want early access to news and updates? Join our Discord server and be the first to know! 🗼🐾
